{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "aura-verifier-api-v1",
    "name": "Aura Verifier API",
    "description": "Complete Postman collection for the Aura Network Third-Party Verifier SDK REST API.\n\n## Overview\n\nThis collection provides endpoints for:\n- **Verification**: Verify credential presentations from QR codes\n- **Age Checks**: Quick 21+ and 18+ verification\n- **Human Verification**: Anti-bot checks\n- **Batch Operations**: Verify multiple presentations\n- **Credential Status**: Check credential validity\n- **DID Resolution**: Resolve Decentralized Identifiers\n- **Trust Score**: Get Aura Trust Score\n\n## Authentication\n\nAll requests require an API key in the `X-API-Key` header.\n\nSet the `api_key` variable in your environment.\n\n## Networks\n\n- **Mainnet**: `https://api.aurablockchain.org/v1`\n- **Testnet**: `https://testnet-api.aurablockchain.org/v1`\n- **Local**: `http://localhost:3000/v1`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Verification",
      "description": "Credential verification endpoints",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Verify Presentation",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
